Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.88,0:01:28.82,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then Takizawa's phone is a\N"magic phone" that can do anything?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.29,0:01:33.22,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's no good! Let's go grab one on the street!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.22,0:01:37.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Anyway, for now, investigate\Nthe data Underpants sent us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't get in touch with him either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay, I'll give it a shot.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.47,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But you guys stay away from Toyosu!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.97,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.97,0:01:49.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The thing is, the missing NEETs
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,have poured into the movie\Ntheater looking for Takizawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.14,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This place is done for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:07.42,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}I'll Kill you for sure, Akira Takizawa!{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.42,0:02:11.88,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Episode 11:\NThe East That Continues On{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.70,0:02:17.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm impressed you knew about this place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.77,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I saw it in the real estate data.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.77,0:02:22.77,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are we going to be okay\Nhiding in a place like this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.77,0:02:26.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's impossible to reason\Nwith furious naked guys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:34.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They're politely collecting their\Ncell phones, even though it's so cold.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So the phones are the most\Nimportant things to them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hello.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.23,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, Kazuomi? We're going to head there after all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:50.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think it'll go faster if we\Ncheck out that data together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:56.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But is there really going\Nto be a sixty-missile attack?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.14,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And if there is, what can we do about it now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:04.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After all, we don't have magic phones.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:13.45,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't think Takizawa saved the\Npeople because he had a magic phone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He was just trying to do what had to be done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.40,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then why did he erase his own memories?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.90,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why are all those NEETs angry at him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.60,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He's right, Saki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:30.41,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They wouldn't be so pissed\Nif he hadn't done something!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.41,0:03:36.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi, Takizawa didn't just protect\Nthe people from the missiles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To protect the 20,000 NEETs who\Nwere being regarded with suspicion
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,because they helped him with the evacuation,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.98,0:03:46.15,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he became the sole bad guy\Nand then erased his memories.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:50.66,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After he got that phone, Takizawa\Nused the information he got online
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and gathered an elite force to\Nsuccessfully evacuate the people
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,using means just barely within the law.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you're saying that elite\Nforce was the 20,000 NEETs?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:12.18,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But afterwards, those he rescued\Nstarted complaining via the media.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.18,0:04:16.15,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,People asked how he and the\Nothers knew about the missiles...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...and whether they'd had ulterior motives.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.52,0:04:24.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even they didn't know whether\Nthe missiles would really come,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.89,0:04:29.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,so apparently some of them used\Nthe opportunity to steal things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.37,0:04:36.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Still, most of them were excited by\Nthe fact that they'd saved citizens.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the citizens who'd lost\Neverything in the missile attacks
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:44.65,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,couldn't dispel the cloud\Nof doubt in their hearts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.65,0:04:48.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then the people who'd\Nbeen observing the situation
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:52.65,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,started using the internet\Nto slander the evacuees.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:59.66,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's one reason the incident\Nbecame more complex and bizarre.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.66,0:05:04.90,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So Takizawa used several fake names\Nto gather the NEETs in Toyosu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.34,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and in order to direct the brunt\Nof the anger toward himself,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:12.17,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he told them he'd been the one\Nbehind the missile terrorism.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think that's why they know him\Nby several different names,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and why they're so openly angry at him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:23.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,After that, he sent them\Nto Dubai for three months
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,to hide them from the spotlight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.76,0:05:32.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Most people are irresponsible,\Nchanging their opinions easily
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.29,0:05:36.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,based on unconfirmed\Ninformation or convenient rumors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa was betrayed by the\Npeople he wanted to protect most,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.64,0:05:48.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and he lost hope, and that's why\Nhe had to erase his memories.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Has he remembered that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.08,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.08,0:05:58.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But this time, we have to do something\Nabout the missile attack ourselves.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.09,0:06:02.42,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why should you have to see it that way?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.42,0:06:07.83,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Even if Takizawa is really a\Ngood person, he's a plain idiot!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:13.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Someone who screws up even with\Na phone like that has to be an idiot!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:20.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think the destinations of the\Nmissiles are in the data Itazu sent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:27.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just like Takizawa did on Careless Monday,\Nif we post that on the net...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.28,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,True.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In today's world, people get arrested\Nfor a single line announcing a murder.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.09,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We'll probably get some kind of reaction
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.09,0:06:39.19,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,if we say there'll be a missile attack.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.19,0:06:40.53,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.30,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's currently impossible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.04,0:06:53.53,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The zombies have Itazu's data!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.21,0:07:00.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry! I left your PC on the bar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.55,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There! This is it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.19,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.72,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right here. This guy is holding it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.72,0:07:12.82,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah. But how do we get it back?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.13,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I have a proposal!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.13,0:07:20.74,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Perhaps we should strip! It would\Nalso be a way to go on the offensive!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.24,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh? Why strip?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sir, the best place to hide a tree is in a forest!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.54,0:07:30.14,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think the best way to blend in with\Nthe naked NEETs would be to get naked!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No way, no way, no way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.83,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They don't notice us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Our strategy is a huge success.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.94,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Looks like it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get over here! It's too late to hesitate now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.58,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, true, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whoa, for real?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:13.45,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have to meet up with\NHirasawa and the others somehow!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.89,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we run through them really fast,\Nwe might actually be okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Whoa, girls!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.88,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You found a PC?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.88,0:08:37.61,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, but it's password-protected...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.88,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let me see it for a second.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.72,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You guys have hair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And you're really pale.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.63,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.26,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Run!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.47,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They're following us...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:10.31,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I-It's okay. They're probably\Nonly interested in 2D girls.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.25,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi, catch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi, just keep going!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,S-Saki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.44,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi, why are you naked?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.38,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't touch the computer to it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.32,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, the hell?! I just went to\Nthe trouble of getting it back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry! But right now, we need Itazu's data!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.56,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This way! Hurry, get inside!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sis!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sis!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Good job making it here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Never mind, hurry up and get the data!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Do Not Leave Open{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.98,0:10:23.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm pretty sure I remember\Nthere being some stuff in red.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Attack Japan\Nwith missiles\Nto restart it\Nfrom the\NPostwar Era{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.01,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Hack surveillance satellite and change\Nimage feed to provoke preemptive attack.\NHack Tomahawk missiles deployed on cruiser{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Fire 60 Tomahawk missiles\NTargets:\NKasumigaseki\NThe Diet Building\NRoppongi on cruiser{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Diet Building and Kasumigaseki are in here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.73,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's split up. First, send this to our cell phones.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.94,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait! No way...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Look at this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}Ikebukuro,\NToyosu,\NGunma{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.40,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Toyosu?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.22,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.06,0:11:12.40,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Testing, testing...\NI'm currently testing the camera.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.43,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,--It's Takizawa!\N--It's Takizawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:22.78,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hi, Johnnys! There's a reason\NI gathered you here today!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.78,0:11:27.45,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And that is to kill you who know\Nthe truth about Careless Monday,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.45,0:11:31.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,as well as all the citizens\Nwho tried to criticize me,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,with a new missile attack!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.49,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's a lie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.32,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you talking about, Takizawa?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.76,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's no way you'd do something like that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why would you tell such a lie?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.30,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is not a lie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:50.74,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,However, there is still a slim\Nchance for you to survive!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All Johnnys who want to live,\Nstart by assembling on the roof!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.27,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.95,0:12:03.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's just mean, saying we\Ncan't get Juiz after all this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry, but you're your own\Nresponsibility from here on out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.99,0:12:12.63,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,However, I plan to search for Mr. Outside again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:16.82,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If I'm able to find him, let's meet again then.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.77,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.94,0:12:29.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You got set up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.35,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I guess I mean you went too far.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:37.62,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What if he's the Supporter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mr. Mononobe told you to launch\Nthe eleventh missile, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.39,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saying you should eliminate the NEETs
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,who were living witnesses\Nto the incident, or whatever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.36,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,My condolences.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.36,0:12:52.30,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But man, that Number 9 is entertaining.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.13,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think he'll pull something again this time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.90,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's too late for him to do anything now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Didn't you hear the news? Two days ago,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.68,0:13:09.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,they changed the strategic\Nprogramming for the Patriot missiles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Leave us behind and escape!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.99,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We can't! The fire shutters are closed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.16,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Can't we get out that way?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm telling you, you can't!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.93,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can't all fit in here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Osugi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.21,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.42,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you Osugi?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.95,0:14:20.25,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You've got guts. You're just like I imagined.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.00,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa, wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:38.24,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The truth is, you came here\Nto save everyone, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.24,0:14:42.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're going to play the bad guy\Nall by yourself again, and save us...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.11,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So you listened over the\Nphone all the way to the end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah. But then my battery ran out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.45,0:15:28.79,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When I went back to Itazu's afterwards,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.79,0:15:31.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,he said he'd sent the logs to Hirasawa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.86,0:15:37.03,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And I figured you guys were sure\Nto come here if you read them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Takizawa, do you remember...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.84,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Glad you all got back here, guys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.84,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the missiles will be\Ncoming at us pretty soon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.84,0:15:54.15,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This time, you have to post a\Nway to intercept the missiles
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.15,0:15:58.15,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,directly to the Eden site!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.65,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hirasawa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.02,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you connect them in series like batteries,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.26,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,they unleash pretty high potential.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.26,0:16:13.20,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sure they'll think up an amazing\Nmiracle, just like on Careless Monday.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.53,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's not like I did that all by myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.66,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs20\fe0\b0\i0\c&Hffffff&\fnPalatino}New Messages{\c}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.25,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Great, kthxbye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.52,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Does he know what that means?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.22,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,--Juiz?\N--Yes, Juiz here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've taken the posts from\Nthe Eden of the East site
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.46,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,and extracted the most effective\Nmethods of avoiding the missiles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.37,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I pray you shall continue\Nto be this country's savior.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thanks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.53,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shall we begin, then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bang.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.37,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So you're okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.54,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is Takizawa making this happen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.54,0:18:00.34,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. Him, and the NEETs here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.71,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is this happening all over Japan right now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.85,0:18:13.95,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When will you come save me, Number 9?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.95,0:18:17.98,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm so good.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:29.64,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Missiles or no missiles,\Nthis country's already headed for death.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Looks like he made it in time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.04,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bang!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.29,0:19:27.75,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What am I, the Sundance Kid?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.86,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Saki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.11,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,--Juiz.\N--Yes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.11,0:19:48.42,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This time I can't smooth things\Nover just by playing a terrorist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.42,0:19:52.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So will you use the rest of my money\Nto make me the king of Japan?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.12,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The king?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.59,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.29,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There are a lot of smart people in this country,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.73,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,but there's nobody to\Ntake on the thankless roles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.83,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't really want to do it either, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.96,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There was one girl who believed in me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.68,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Accepted. Noblesse oblige.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.51,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I pray you shall be a splendid\Nprince the next time we meet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I hope I'm the same then as I am now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.81,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oh, and Juiz...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.97,0:20:45.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Damn, there's no gold ring\Non this merry-go-round.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:04.69,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And so he became a prince...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.18,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...in this country with no king.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The night is a seal
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,s2s_def_sub_set,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future